    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>踏上一场有趣的冒险，你被一位强大的神召唤，执行一项任务：找回从这位神那里偷走的圣球。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243590/extras/37a652c315f046ae6cc3bbb6ba3633a0.poster.avif?t=1758473960\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243590/extras/37a652c315f046ae6cc3bbb6ba3633a0.webm?t=1758473960\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243590/extras/37a652c315f046ae6cc3bbb6ba3633a0.mp4?t=1758473960\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>被盗的球。</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >拾起散落在不同关卡的球。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有多个不同颜色的球需要抓取。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >找到它们，抓取它们并将它们放到箱子里。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243590/extras/ef65f95996958cc64ecab9aafad98736.poster.avif?t=1758473960\" width=600 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243590/extras/ef65f95996958cc64ecab9aafad98736.webm?t=1758473960\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243590/extras/ef65f95996958cc64ecab9aafad98736.mp4?t=1758473960\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>将球存放在盒子里，将球归还给负责这些球的神</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个盒子的颜色与球相同。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >盒子是球到达神的门户。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当你存储的球达到一定数量时，就会发生一些事情。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243590/extras/421d293b8c94ae84410d78a3f9b24908.poster.avif?t=1758473960\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243590/extras/421d293b8c94ae84410d78a3f9b24908.webm?t=1758473960\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243590/extras/421d293b8c94ae84410d78a3f9b24908.mp4?t=1758473960\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>根据盒子中存放的球数来解锁新关卡。</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个关卡都有不同的视觉效果。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在每个关卡中，需要解决的挑战的复杂性都会增加。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个关卡都有特定数量的球需要收集。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每增加一个新关卡，需要捕获的球数也会增加。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243590/extras/c4c442281f1637c2ed93cc439a311af0.poster.avif?t=1758473960\" width=600 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243590/extras/c4c442281f1637c2ed93cc439a311af0.webm?t=1758473960\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243590/extras/c4c442281f1637c2ed93cc439a311af0.mp4?t=1758473960\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>每个级别的挑战都会变得更加困难。</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个谜题都有一个学习曲线，一个谜题会教你一些关于下一个谜题的知识。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有些谜题是让你自由进入球，有些谜题是让你自由离开关卡。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你需要完成谜题才能在游戏中前进。</p></li></ul>",
